---
import { format } from "date-fns";

import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import Link from "../components/Link.astro";
import HomeLink from "../components/HomeLink.astro";

const lastUpdated = "2025-07-17";
---

<Layout
  description="Hisam â€” is a software developer, voracious reader, active (trying his best) writer"
>
  <div class="mt-24">
    <HomeLink />
    <h1 class="font-instrument mt-4 text-3xl font-medium">Now</h1>
    <p class="font-instrument text-lg italic">
      Last updated: {format(new Date(lastUpdated), "dd MMM yyyy")}
    </p>

    <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
      <p>
        I have been trying my best to have a lot of meaningful things to do
        every moment of my life. Here's what I have been up to lately:
      </p>
      <ul class="ml-5 list-disc">
        <li>Living in BSD City, ID;</li>
        <li>
          Product & engineering at <Link
            href="https://www.persol-group.co.jp/en/"
            target="_blank">PERSOL APAC</Link
          >;
        </li>
        <li>
          Reading a lot of books, articles, and newsletters (mostly from the <Link
            href="https://news.ycombinator.com"
            target="_blank">Hacker News</Link
          >);
          <ul class="ml-5">
            <li>
              Currently reading <Link
                href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/138825075-the-book"
                target="_blank">The Book</Link
              >;
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          Writing more:
          <ul class="ml-5 list-disc">
            <li>
              On my <Link href="/journals" target="_blank">journal</Link> and on
              <Link href="/uses">my pen and paper</Link>;
            </li>
            <li>
              Grow my <Link
                href="https://notes.andymatuschak.org/Evergreen_notes"
                target="_blank">Evergreen notes</Link
              > with <Link href="https://obsidian.md" target="_blank"
                >Obsidian</Link
              >;
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          Building <Link href="https://cakeauth.com" target="_blank"
            >CakeAuth</Link
          > - an authentication as a service;
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
